name: Pontem Liquidswap
description: Liquidswap by Pontem is the most popular decentralized exchange (DEX) on Aptos and the Move ecosystem. It's built on Move for maximum security and performance, with multiple audits. With Liquidswap, you can swap tokens, and earn through yield farming, staking, and liquidity pools. Pontem is a product studio working toward global financial inclusion powered by blockchains. We are partnered with Aptos to build foundational dApps and other infrastructure which enable adoption of their L1, such as development tooling, EVMs, AMMs, and more
